    {
      "id": "RQ-0002",
      "status": "done",
      "title": "Add prompt/context budgeting before Cursor Agent.send",
      "priority": "high",
      "tags": [
        "context",
        "cursor-sdk",
        "performance"
      ],
      "scope": [
        "src/context.ts",
        "src/cursor-provider.ts",
        "test/context.test.ts",
        "test/cursor-provider.test.ts"
      ],
      "evidence": [
        "src/context.ts:70-100 serializes every pi message/tool result into one Cursor prompt.",
        "src/cursor-provider.ts:585-586 estimates prompt tokens after building the full prompt but does not trim against model.contextWindow.",
        "Long sessions or large tool outputs can exceed Cursor context despite accurate model metadata."
      ],
      "plan": [
        "Design a budgeted transcript builder that preserves system instructions and the latest user request.",
        "Trim or summarize oldest turns and large tool outputs with an output-token reserve.",
        "Add tests for oversized histories and oversized tool results.",
        "Run npm test and npm run typecheck."
      ],
      "notes": [
        "Started by agent to add prompt/context budgeting before Cursor Agent.send.",
        "Added model-derived prompt input budgeting before Cursor Agent.send. Preserves system/tool-boundary instructions and latest user request, keeps recent history that fits, omits older oversized history/tool output with an omission notice, and reserves estimated image tokens. Validated with npm test -- test/context.test.ts, npm test -- test/cursor-provider.test.ts, npm test, npm run typecheck. Reviewer subagent reported no material findings after image-budget fix."
      ],
