        "test/cursor-provider.test.ts:476-522 currently expects firstText to be empty after Cursor emits pre-tool text."
      ],
      "plan": [
        "Queue or emit pre-tool text into the first replay turn before the native tool call.",
        "Update tests to assert the pre-tool assistant text is preserved.",
        "Verify native replay still mirrors pi toolUse/toolResult turn shape.",
